quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,62,sun rakho ke jo khuda ke dost hain un ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  10,63,( yani ) jo log imaan laaye aur parhaizgaar rahay
  10,64,un ke liye duniya ki zindagi mein bhi basharat hai aur akhirat mein bhi. khuda ki baatein badalti nahi. yahi to barri kamyabi hai
  10,65,aur ( ae paighambar ) un logon ki baton se aazurda nah hona ( kyunkay ) izzat sab khuda hi ki hai woh ( sab kuch ) santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  10,66,sun rakho ke jo makhlooq asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai sab khuda ke ( bande aur is ke mamlook ) hain. aur yeh jo khuda ke siwa ( apne banaye hue ) sharikon ko pkarte hain. woh ( kisi aur cheez ke ) peechay nahi chaltay. sirf zan ke peechay chaltay hain aur mehez atklin dora rahay hain
  10,67,wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai taakay is mein aaraam karo aur roz roshan banaya ( taakay is mein kaam karo ) jo log samaat rakhtay hain un ke liye un mein nishanain hain
  10,68,( baaz log ) kehte hain ke khuda ne beta bana liya hai. is ki zaat ( aulaad se ) pak hai ( aur ) woh be niaz hai. jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai woh sab isi ka hai ( ae iftira o pardazo ) tumahray paas is ( qoul baatil ) ki koi Daleel nahi hai. tum khuda ki nisbat aisi baat kyun kehte ho jo jantay nahi
  10,69,keh do jo log khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhtay hain Falah nahi payen ge
  10,70,( un ke liye jo ) faiday hain duniya mein ( hain ) phir un ko hamari hi taraf lout kar aana hai. is waqt hum un ko shadeed azaab ( ke mazay ) chkhayin ge kyunkay kufar ( ki baatein )kiya karte they
